# M6 P02 — jetpack FX sync test (host) — Glide vs JumpJet coverage.
#
# Pairs with 2p_jet_fx_glide.client.shot. Host runs Glide-wing
# (intermittent pale-cyan wisps); client runs JumpJet (discrete kick
# on each jet press, green-cyan ignition flash, no continuous plume).
#
# Same map + spawns as 2p_jet_fx for camera framing consistency.

window 1280 720
out build/shots/net/2p_jet_fx_glide.host
network host 24202
name HostGlide
map reactor
loadout Trooper "Pulse Rifle" Sidearm Light Glide

spawn_at 400 1176
peer_spawn 1 650 1176

aim 1100 1140

# Glide sustains — hold jet, capture wisps at sustain divisor's
# 4-tick cadence.
at 240 press jet
at 245 shot t245_ignition
at 270 shot t270_sustain
at 320 shot t320_late_sustain
at 340 release jet
at 360 shot t360_falling
at 400 shot t400_grounded_again

at 460 end

contact_sheet sheet cols 3 cell 640 360
